And it's been a struggle,

00:43:29.968 --> 00:43:31.534
it's been a struggle
for his family.

00:43:31.634 --> 00:43:33.734
I know his mother's
taking it very hard.

00:43:33.834 --> 00:43:36.267
DEPUTY: He was in a manic
episode outside of his home.

